{
  "stem": "4570.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was the-- that was the saddest thing, that I went through all that awful mess without really-- it made no sense.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But for me it makes sense, because I could never be so involved in helping exploited and abused animals if I wouldn't have been in that same situation.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I have given my whole life now to-- for many, many, many years, I work in animal welfare because I think that-- I, I think I learned an awful lot in the camp.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And what about learning the fate of your father?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh-- I mean, you knew by the time-- right in Theresienstadt, I knew.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Old people, they, they were the first to go from Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All I knew, that, that his transport went to Treblinka.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My father must have been about 67 or sort of nearly as old as I am.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you know, people were much older at that time than we are now.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I mean, there was just no hope for-- I think anybody who would have been over 55, that, that there was no hope for them.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my mother still had the, the apartment.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not the elaborate that-- when I was born, but in the meantime we moved to a modern, smaller flat.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I learned how to make hand-woven materials.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And some of the boys from Theresienstadt got back their farm and they had sheep, and they had wool and they supplied the wool to me.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I start-- starting having it dyed and making very nice materials.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And because after the war there was nothing, it was terrific black market.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Everything-- I mean, if, if you just little bit with it, you could make a very good living.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And with those materials, I, I really did very well.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
